GLOBAL_LATENCY_DESCRIPTION: change GLOBAL_LATENCY to your lowest usual ping
AUTORHK_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto RHK after GP
GPRHKDelay_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
AUTORHK2_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto RHK after HM
HMRHKDelay_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
RHKKEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for RHK, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
AUTO_COMBO_ATTACK_MOVE_DESCRIPTION: Automatically trigger punch -> block movement combo when you press punch +w
BLOCKKEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for block, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
AUTO_BLOCK_FLIP_KICK_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto block cancel flip kick
AUTO_BLOCK_FLIP_KICK_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
JH_AUTO_HM_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto Haymaker after Jackhammer.
JH_AUTO_HM_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
HM_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Haymaker, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
FLYKICK_AUTO_ONEINCH_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto One Inch after Fly Kick.
FLYKICK_AUTO_ONEINCH_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
ONEINCH_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for One Inch, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
PD_AUTO_CP_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto Counter Punch after Piledriver.
PD_AUTO_CP_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
PD_AUTO_RHK_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto RHK after Piledriver. Cannot be used with PD_AUTO_CP
CP_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Counter Punch, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
HM_AUTO_CP_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto Counter Punch after Haymaker
JH_AUTO_PD_DESCRIPTION: DO NOT USE WITHOUT ROBOTJS - Auto piledriver after jackhammer
PD_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Pile Driver, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
JH_AUTO_PD_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Delay at base aspd in milliseconds
GF_X_DESCRIPTION: Auto use X_KEY when Growing Fury is used. X_KEY must be set. This macro does not work without ROBOTJS.
X_KEY_DESCRIPTION: X Key. Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
Y_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Y Key (keep the same as X_KEY if you don't want a second skill to activate). Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
Z_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Z Key (keep the same as X_KEY if you don't want a second skill to activate). Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
